The speaker is describing the remarkable capabilities of ChatGPT, an artificial intelligence system that interacts with users through text-based tasks. The speaker exemplifies the system's functionality by posing various prompts and discussing the diverse range of responses from ChatGPT. The AI proves its proficiency by generating unique, contextually appropriate responses to each prompt, which can vary each time the same prompt is used. The speaker points out that this variability is due to the probabilistic nature of ChatGPT. In summary, when the speaker mentions that "this is a pretty remarkable system", they are referring to ChatGPT's ability to generate diverse and relevant content based on user prompts.
